omponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"BarComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Bar","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors ("},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), borders (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and effects (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllEffectSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider","type":"topic","title":"OrangeThemeBarCom